{"word":"G940 - βασκαίνω - baskaínō - bas-kah'-ee-no - Bewitch","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βασκαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">baskaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bas-kah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bewitch</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மயக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to speak ill of one, to slander"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Akin to <a href=\"#/G5335 - φάσκω - pháskō - fas'-ko/5335\">G5335</a>; to <i>malign</i>, that is, (by extension) to <i>fascinate</i> (by false representations): - bewitch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}